Sentencas: La1-xSrxGa1-yMgyO3-delta (LSGM) with various x and y levels were prepared and evaluated as a solid oxide fuel cell electrolyte.
Titulo: Effect of sr and mg doping on the property and performance of the La1-xSrxGa1-yMgyO3-δ electrolyte

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity of LSGM was dramatically enhanced with the increase of both the Sr and Mg doping levels.
Titulo: Effect of sr and mg doping on the property and performance of the La1-xSrxGa1-yMgyO3-δ electrolyte

Sentencas: The compositions with 20 mol % Sr and 15-20 mol %
Titulo: Effect of sr and mg doping on the property and performance of the La1-xSrxGa1-yMgyO3-δ electrolyte

Sentencas: Mg were found to possess much higher conductivity than the other compositions at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Effect of sr and mg doping on the property and performance of the La1-xSrxGa1-yMgyO3-δ electrolyte

Sentencas: The optimal composition was La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.83Mg0.17O3-delta with the highest conductivity of 0.177 and 0.087 S/cm at 800 and 700 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Effect of sr and mg doping on the property and performance of the La1-xSrxGa1-yMgyO3-δ electrolyte

Sentencas: The coefficient of thermal expansion (CTE) was measured and shrinkage probably due to phase transition was observed in the CTE curve.
Titulo: Effect of sr and mg doping on the property and performance of the La1-xSrxGa1-yMgyO3-δ electrolyte

Sentencas: The correlation between the phase transition, thermal expansion, and electrical conductivity was discussed.
Titulo: Effect of sr and mg doping on the property and performance of the La1-xSrxGa1-yMgyO3-δ electrolyte

Sentencas: The performance of various LSGM compositions was assessed through the electrolyte-supported cells using a La0.4Ce0.6O1.8(LDC)+Ni anode over a LDC buffer layer and a SrCo0.8Fe0.2O-delta (SCF) cathode.
Titulo: Effect of sr and mg doping on the property and performance of the La1-xSrxGa1-yMgyO3-δ electrolyte

Sentencas: The single cell with the La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.83Mg0.17O3-delta electrolyte gave the best performance among all the cells, i.e., a maximum power density of 1.23 and 0.66 W/cm(2) in wet H-2 at 800 and 700 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Effect of sr and mg doping on the property and performance of the La1-xSrxGa1-yMgyO3-δ electrolyte

Sentencas: A relatively stable cell performance with < 10% loss in power density was observed over 500 h under a constant current density of 735 mA/cm(2) at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Effect of sr and mg doping on the property and performance of the La1-xSrxGa1-yMgyO3-δ electrolyte

Sentencas: The power loss was mainly due to the increase in cathode overpotential.
Titulo: Effect of sr and mg doping on the property and performance of the La1-xSrxGa1-yMgyO3-δ electrolyte

Sentencas: Co was found to diffuse across the interface from the SCF cathode into the LSGM electrolyte during the long-term testing, which might lead to a Co deficiency in the cathode and thus contribute to the observed degradation in the cathode as well as the cell performance.
Titulo: Effect of sr and mg doping on the property and performance of the La1-xSrxGa1-yMgyO3-δ electrolyte
